social_posts.post_text: African team in the semifinals of the World Cup. Congratulations to Morocco. What an unbelievable team performance. To see an African coach lead them and a inspiring. I have been watching World Cups since 1986 and this is one of the most iconic moments for African soccer. So proud of my Moroccan brothers and sister🤲🏿⚽️🇲🇦. #Mabrook

Rest in Heaven King. The GOAT of football. Thank you for inspiring a kid from 🇬🇲. Some of things we are seeing today you already did. Winning World Cup and being the best player at the age 17 was and will still be unheard of.

Thank you for all the memories and the way you transcended the game of football. The one and only Edson Arantes Do Nacimento.🖤⚽️🤲🏿 #TBE #kingoffootball👑⚽️ #oneandonlylove

As 2022 journey comes to end I look back at a year filled with lots of blessings. Thank you to my family and friends for their endless love and support. To the new friendships made thank you for being part of my life.

As 2023 journey is about to begin I wish my family and friends a year full of blessings, health, joy, happiness and prosperity.

Whatever journey is bestowed upon you attack it with full confidence and happiness to conquer it. 

Life is a blessing and we are blessed to live this beautiful life with love and happiness surrounding us. Be safe and see you all in the new year🖤🤲🏿
